The Intergovernmental Negotiating Body is, per the World Health Assembly decision, operating based on the principles of inclusiveness, transparency, efficiency, Member State leadership and consensus. Public updates are provided at all relevant steps of the process. The WHO website is the main source of information.A report will be submitted to the World Health Assembly in 2023. The final decision on whatever pandemic accord is agreed will happen in open plenary in the World Health Assembly in 2024.More information on the INB 
